<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.5.8">
<l>kaiyuṇaṉ mukamvaikku naiyumeṉ ṟaṉṉaiya rumuṉitir</l>
<l>maikoṇ māṭat tirukkuṟuṅkuṭi nampiyai nāṉkaṇṭapiṉ</l>
<l>ceyyatāmaraik kaṇṇu malkuluñ ciṟṟiṭai yumvaṭivu</l>
<l>moyyanīḷkuḻa ṟāḻnta tōḷkaḷum pāviyēṉ muṉṉiṟkumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“She keeps [her] good face in [her] hands, languishes”, so you all disapprove, mothers.</l>
<l>After I saw Nampi of Tirukkuṟuṅkuṭi with storied mansions up to the clouds,</l>
<l>the red lotus eyes, the hips, the narrow waist, the shape</l>
<l>and the shoulders on which dense long locks hang stand before me evildoer.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
